WEBVTT

00:07:59.011 --> 00:08:01.122
Let's play out a scenario.

00:08:01.146 --> 00:08:03.859
Let's say that you are a parent,

00:08:03.883 --> 00:08:06.881
and you need 25 minutes
of uninterrupted time

00:08:06.905 --> 00:08:08.463
to get dinner ready.

00:08:08.487 --> 00:08:12.146
And in order to do that,
you hand a tablet to your three-year-old.

00:08:12.170 --> 00:08:15.147
Now, this is a moment
where you probably feel very guilty

00:08:15.171 --> 00:08:16.570
about what you just did.

00:08:17.745 --> 00:08:19.745
But now imagine this:

00:08:19.769 --> 00:08:22.819
Twenty minutes later,
you receive a text message.

00:08:22.843 --> 00:08:25.817
on that cell phone
that's always within arm's reach.

00:08:25.841 --> 00:08:30.379
And it says: "Alex just matched
five rhyming words.